* ABOUT
    D3 is a user-friendly cross-platfrom scene graph based OpenGL graphics engine.
    
* REQUIREMENTS
    libpng 
        - for included XCode project, libs in /usr/local/lib
        - for included XCode project, headers in /usr/local/include
        
* BASIC USAGE
    Create Scene.
    Create Renderer.
    Render Scene each frame using Renderer.

* NOTE
    This is a work in progress.